tap.metadata

Class TableSetParser.ForeignKey

  • java.lang.Object
    • tap.metadata.TableSetParser.ForeignKey
  • Enclosing class:
    TableSetParser

    protected static class TableSetParser.ForeignKey
extends java.lang.Object

    Intermediary representation of a Foreign Key.

    An instance of this class lets save all information provided in the XML document and needed to create the corresponding TAP metadata (TAPForeignKey) at the end of XML document parsing, once all available tables are listed.

    Since:
    2.0
    Version:
    2.0 (02/2015)
    Author:
    Grégory Mantelet (ARI)
    See Also:
    TableSetParser.parseFKey(XMLStreamReader), TableSetParser.parse(InputStream)
